Appointment Utilization Tip Sheet Developed by: Matthew Moreno Updated: 2022-08-12

1 - Utilization Overview

Views utilization for all of SACHS, Location, and Department.

2 - Provider Utilization

Views utilization for all of providers organized by Location & Department.

3 - Block Utilization

Measures utilization by appointment block type & provider.

1. Utilization Overview In Detail

 

 

1. # of Booked Openings

Total # of Booked openings across all sites for the given Start & End dates provided.

 

2. # of Available Openings

Total # of available openings across all sites for the given Start & End dates provided.

 

3. Utilization %

Site wide utilization given by the following formula:

\[\frac{Part \space \space 1}{Part \space \space 2} \longrightarrow \frac{\# \space \space of \space \space Booked \space \space Openings}{\# \space \space of \space \space Available \space \space Openings} \longrightarrow \frac{675}{793} = 85.1\% \]

Location Utilization

 

 

Utilization rates for each site for the given Start & End dates provided.
